{"tid":851125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用國旗做垃圾袋？ 官方：清潔工不是刻意","createTime":"2018-10-07T02:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T09:37:46.000Z","uid":1661,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c8986bcbb764e293e85595ece7bb436df9e7c6ba","tid":851125,"uid":1661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538820497_936f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538820497_936f.jpg&h=9797ebd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河北省有清潔工竟用國旗作垃圾袋。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n有微博網民於昨日曝料，指河北省保定市定興收費站，及京昆高速定興收費站，有人竟用國旗做麻袋裝垃圾，稱「國慶節看到這一幕，氣死人，誰來管管？」定興縣委宣傳部事後表示，據警方調查，高速服務區清潔員用舊國旗包裹雜物，事後國旗已被妥善收好。<br />\n<br />\n定興縣委宣傳部回應內地傳媒查詢時表示，事發於京昆高速定興西服務區，路過遊客拍到國旗被當麻袋裝雜物，將相片上傳網上。當地派出所立即調查，初步查明事件發生於5日下午1時左右，京昆高速定興西服務區清潔員賈某某、王某某，因收集的雜物無處盛放，便用了一面舊國旗包裹，放在服務區南側，事後國旗被妥善收好，目前案件正在進一步調查中。<br />\n<br />\n定興縣委宣傳部有關領導表示，此事應是因清潔員不懂得國旗的意義和有關法律責任而引起，但不是刻意為之。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181006/58764525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58764525&d=VXAYx0S8Fq2ve3j0i6IwnzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=d5440c40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58764525&h=0c1e6258\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181006/58764525</a>"},{"pid":"b46ab88d09a14ef9fd4e4bf5f48df966adef1b71","tid":851125,"uid":126731,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"HO BALL<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c19bcaa548fd670fd48ec956662c0f3bcd0d2d4","tid":851125,"uid":194079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:50:45.000Z","msg":"大陸好多人其實不滿中共"},{"pid":"c4f6f5a1a